// SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
pragma solidity ^0.8.20;

contract VideoLicenseAgreement {
    string constant public agreement = "" 
        "Licensing Agreement

" 
        "1. Grant of License
" 
        "- You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the video [Video Title] for the purpose of creating derivative video content.

" 
        "2. Usage Limitations
" 
        "- This license is for non-commercial use only.
" 
        "- You must provide attribution to [Your Name/Your Channel] in any derivative works.

" 
        "3. Duration
" 
        "- The license is valid for [Duration] from the date of purchase.

" 
        "4. Payment Terms
" 
        "- The license fee is [Amount], payable via [Payment Method].

" 
        "5. Prohibited Uses
" 
        "- You may not redistribute, sublicense, or resell the video.
" 
        "- The video may not be used in any content that promotes hate speech, violence, or illegal activities.

" 
        "6. Termination
" 
        "- This agreement will terminate automatically if you breach any of its terms.

" 
        "7. Governing Law
" 
        "- This agreement shall be governed by the laws of [Your Country/State].

" 
        "8. Contact Information
" 
        "- For any questions regarding this agreement, please contact [Your Contact Information].

" 
        "Signature
" 
        "- [Your Signature/Your Company's Signature]

";

    constructor() {}
}
